snippet.textDisplay: This was one of the best experiences of my life! Being a part of Lizzo’s all black/brown, all woman orchestra for the Grammy’s was everything!!  Rarely are black classical musicians highlighted in this way, we are usually the only face in a group and deal with disgusting levels of discrimination, so for Lizzo to intentionally give us this platform was everything!  I am honored to have been a part of something so historic and beautiful!  Thank you Lizzo!!
